stories.title: South Africa crush hapless Zimbabwe
stories.summary:
The only way is up: Doug Marillier skys an attempted hook and falls to Makhaya Ntini    
 
 
 From a neutral spectator's point of view, this was one-day cricket at its most unappetising
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Martin Williamson
